WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.266 --> 00:00:02.533
What? You say that Rongfei's heart is lacking?

2
00:00:02.533 --> 00:00:03.500
What’s happening?

3
00:00:03.666 --> 00:00:05.366
Yesterday, yesterday

4
00:00:05.366 --> 00:00:08.333
My sister was afraid I’d steal her spotlight if I became a Xiunu

5
00:00:08.333 --> 00:00:09.900
So she pushed me into the lake

6
00:00:10.166 --> 00:00:12.800
If it weren’t for our family’s servants arriving in time

7
00:00:13.733 --> 00:00:15.466
I wouldn't have been able to see Your Majesty

8
00:00:15.466 --> 00:00:17.600
You say Wufei pushed you into the water?

9
00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:19.200
Yes, Your Majesty, I didn’t expect it either

10
00:00:19.200 --> 00:00:20.600
My sister turned out to be so cruel

11
00:00:20.600 --> 00:00:23.866
Where's the imperial physician? Why hasn’t the physician arrived yet?

12
00:00:24.533 --> 00:00:27.300
Your Majesty, this is the fastest I could get here

13
00:00:27.300 --> 00:00:29.766
Enough talk, hurry and check on Rongfei’s condition

14
00:00:29.800 --> 00:00:31.400
If anything happens to her

15
00:00:31.400 --> 00:00:34.500
I’ll have the entire Taiyuan buried with her! Alright, alright!

16
00:00:39.900 --> 00:00:41.900
Did Your Ladyship fall into the water yesterday?

17
00:00:42.133 --> 00:00:43.400
It’s clear she caught a cold

18
00:00:43.400 --> 00:00:46.633
The emotional shock was too much for her body, which caused her to faint

19
00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:49.400
As I thought

20
00:00:51.733 --> 00:00:54.500
When I arrived, Rongfei said she fell into the water

21
00:00:54.500 --> 00:00:57.133
I was puzzled, now I see it was your doing

22
00:00:57.133 --> 00:00:59.033
Your Majesty, please let me explain

23
00:00:59.066 --> 00:01:00.200
I’m the victim here

24
00:01:00.200 --> 00:01:01.000
How dare you!

25
00:01:01.900 --> 00:01:03.333
If your heart weren’t filled with malice

26
00:01:03.333 --> 00:01:04.666
If you hadn’t pushed her to the brink

27
00:01:04.666 --> 00:01:06.066
Why would she have lashed out at you?

28
00:01:06.066 --> 00:01:07.766
Clearly, you’re the one with a venomous heart

29
00:01:08.066 --> 00:01:11.366
Your Majesty, please let me explain, I...

30
00:01:15.333 --> 00:01:16.466
Plotting and slandering

31
00:01:16.466 --> 00:01:18.833
Such actions cannot be tolerated before the emperor. Guards!

32
00:01:21.366 --> 00:01:23.800
No, Your Majesty, I'm being wronged!

33
00:01:23.966 --> 00:01:24.900
Listen to my explanation!

34
00:01:25.100 --> 00:01:28.400
Take her away and give her twenty heavy strokes with the rod!

35
00:01:28.666 --> 00:01:30.266
Your Majesty, listen to my explanation!

36
00:01:30.266 --> 00:01:32.466
Your Majesty, I’m being wronged!

37
00:01:35.166 --> 00:01:36.800
Imperial physician, come quickly!

38
00:01:43.800 --> 00:01:44.600
Ah...

39
00:01:45.366 --> 00:01:46.166
Ah...

40
00:01:48.400 --> 00:01:50.900
Your Majesty, Rongfei is fine

41
00:01:50.900 --> 00:01:52.000
She’ll wake up soon

42
00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:54.233
Very well, you may leave

43
00:01:55.733 --> 00:01:58.033
Help! Save me!

44
00:01:59.900 --> 00:02:01.800
Ah...

45
00:02:01.800 --> 00:02:02.966
Who's outside?

46
00:02:02.966 --> 00:02:05.033
What’s going on? Who’s laughing so wickedly?
